title: The Best of the Dan Patrick Show
itunes:title: The Best of the Dan Patrick Show
description:
Covino & Rich are filling in for Dan Patrick and have fun on your Wednesday, talking random Willie Randolph stats and the strange who don't use coffee. Is it better to burn out or fade away? Plus, Covino has a deep thought, called the "Jim Edmonds Theory!" #FSRWeekends
